title: Rep. Ocasio-Cortez And Stephen Eat Ben & Jerry's | Colbert Classic
description:
In honor of the upcoming midterm elections, here's Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez in 2019 telling Stephen about her first few weeks in Congress over a couple pints of ice cream.
